Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:09.62,OPC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}因為隨之而來的責任之重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:14.13,OPC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}果熟落地　歸於塵土
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:17.05,OPC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you 就連傷痛
